copy desktop.wav to /etc/sound/
Then add to the last line in icewm startup: aplay /etc/sound/desktop.wav 
______________________________________________________________________________________________________
Change TimeFormat=" %a %x %l:%M:%S %p " in icewm preferences
______________________________________________________________________________________________________
Edit /etc/timidity/timdity.cfg
comment out line 32 source/ect/timidity/freepats.cfg
uncomment line 35 source/etc/timidity/fluidr3_gm.cfg
_____________________________________________________________________________________________________
change /user/share/menu/vkeybd line 6 to command="/usr/bin/vkeybd --addr 128:0" (This menu item still did not work after adding the address, that's why I went with the desktop entry) 
_________________________________________________________________________________________________-__
Add to desktop: 

[Desktop Entry]

Name=Virtual MIDI Keyboard
Comment=MIDI Virtual Keyboard
Icon=vkeybd

Type=Application
Categories=AudioVideo;Audio;

Exec=vkeybd --addr 128:0
Terminal=false
_____________________________________________________________________________________________________


copy flaming_trebleclef.jpg to user/share/wallpaper
copy  Music_Background.jpg to user/share/wallpaper
copy hd_wall_music.jpg to user/share/wallpaper

Change user/share/antix-settings/wallpaper/wallpaper-list.conf to the following.
 
fluxbox=/usr/share/wallpaper/flaming_trebleclef.jpg
rox-fluxbox=/usr/share/wallpaper/flaming_trebleclef.jpg
space-fluxbox=/usr/share/wallpaper/flaming_trebleclef.jpg
icewm=/usr/share/wallpaper/Music_Background.jpg
rox-icewm=/usr/share/wallpaper/Music_Background.jpg
space-icewm=/usr/share/wallpaper/Music_Background.jpg
jwm=/usr/share/wallpaper/hd_wall_music.jpg
rox-jwm=/usr/share/wallpaper/Music_Background.jpg
space-jwm=/usr/share/wallpaper/hd_wall_music.jpg
